Nodes.Comment: At step 3/4, run between them and serve Ale/Meat. Once the two Meat are done just run Ale to 3.
You can [weapon-swap] fix the Drilling Machines (you get a Boulder from them). Also, if you drop the Boulder midcast ([weapon-swap]) you can use the same Boulder for all holes.
Don't bother with the Testing Kits. just kill Skale and click all Dispensers.
Talk to Heart NPC and spam dialog 1 (Easy). Get a Jar and check your Boon, make sure to catch the correct bugs. Use skil 1 on Flying bugs and 2 on Ground bugs.
Grab a Water Bucket and water all Bushes and Vegetables.
Chop the trees. Start cutting but [weapon-swap] and run back to the Fire Pit. You will get a stick in your hands after a few seconds.

DetachedNodes.Comment: 1: Give him all the Meat nearby.
2: Give him all the Meat nearby.
3: Give him Ale from the nearby cart.
4: Give him the two Meat that's next to 3.
